  "text": "vector was generated as previously described [CITATION_1] . Myc-tagged human wild-type (WT) and mutant CRMP2 (S522A, T555A) [CITATION_2] contained in a pCAGGS vector, and dominant negative RhoK [pEF-BOS-Myc-RB/PH (TT)] vector [CITATION_3] were kindly provided by Dr Kaibuchi's lab. TTBK1  siRNA  sequences  (clone  19; 5'-GCTCTTAAGGACGAAACCAACATGAGTGG-3') were selected and subcloned into pVL-EGFP-Puro vectors. Upstream of the green fluorescence protein (GFP) coding sequences, siRNA sequences were inserted into pSuper siRNA vectors at the Hind III restriction site.",
